PN,30201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,FAirlines will be allowed to group
OL,7,Fpassengers from different flights onto
OL,8,Ffewer planes to tackle shortages on
OL,9,Fjet fuel, the Department of Transport
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe temporary rule change will allow
OL,13,Fairline carriers to consolidate
OL,14,Fflights on routes where there are
OL,15,Fmultiple trips to the same destination
OL,16,Fon the same day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,FPassengers could therefore find
OL,7,Fthemselves moved from their original
OL,8,Fflights to other carriers to avoid
OL,9,Fplanes flying half-empty, or the
OL,10,Fjourney being cancelled altogether.
OL,12,FThe measure is intended to give
OL,13,Fpassengers "greater confidence" in
OL,14,Ftravelling abroad, by helping airlines
OL,15,Fto lock in their schedules earlier,
OL,16,Fthe DfT said.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,F"There are no immediate supply issues,
OL,7,Fbut we're preparing now to give
OL,8,Ffamilies long-term certainty and avoid
OL,9,Funnecessary disruption at the
OL,10,Fdeparture gate this summer," Transport
OL,11,FSecretary Heidi Alexander said.
OL,13,F"This legislation will give airlines
OL,14,Fthe tools to adjust flights in good
OL,15,Ftime if they need to, which helps
OL,16,Fprotect passengers and businesses."
OL,18,FAirlines will also be able to cancel
OL,19,Ftheir flights weeks in advance,
OL,20,Fwithout losing take off and landing
OL,21,Fslots at busy airports, the DfT said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,FThe plan has drawn some criticism from
OL,7,Fthe Conservatives and consumer group
OL,8,FWhich?, who said rules already exist
OL,9,Fto allow airlines to move customers to
OL,10,Fnew flights, so long as they give them
OL,11,Fmore than 14 days' notice.
OL,13,FRory Boland, editor of Which? Travel,
OL,14,Fcalled for the government to ensure
OL,15,Fpassengers' rights are not weakened by
OL,16,Fthe temporary changes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,F"It's only for cancellations within 14
OL,7,Fdays that compensation is payable,
OL,8,Frightly. It's not fair for the rules
OL,9,Fto now be bent in favour of airlines
OL,10,Fand potentially leave passengers
OL,11,Fholding the bill," Boland said.
OL,13,F"Many passengers will understand that
OL,14,Fdisruptions can occur and may be happy
OL,15,Fto travel a few hours or a day later,
OL,16,Fbut for those on short trips or
OL,17,Fconnecting flights it could mean the
OL,18,Ftrip is no longer worthwhile.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,F"Before any changes are made,
OL,7,Fpassengers need cast-iron assurances
OL,8,Fthat their rights will not be weakened
OL,9,Fand that airlines cannot use reform as
OL,10,Fcover to shift the cost of disruption
OL,11,Fon to travellers."
OL,13,FShadow transport secretary Richard
OL,14,FHolden criticised the move, stating
OL,15,Fthat families could find themselves
OL,16,F"herded on to a different plane, at a
OL,17,Ftime of the airline's choosing" under
OL,18,Fthe plan.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,F"The honest message is that Britain is
OL,7,Fexposed to fuel supply risks that a
OL,8,Fproperly energy-secure country would
OL,9,Fnot face," Holden said.
OL,11,FAirlines in the UK have said they are
OL,12,Fnot currently facing issues with fuel
OL,13,Fsupply, but this could change in a
OL,14,Fmatter of weeks as the US-Israel war
OL,15,Fin Iran continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
