PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777835461
OL,3,CAirlines to group passengers from
OL,4,Cdifferent flights to save on jet fuel
OL,6,FThe Strait of Hormuz, an essential
OL,7,Fwaterway through which a fifth of the
OL,8,Fworld's oil typically passes, has been
OL,9,Falmost entirely closed since the war
OL,10,Fin Iran began, and is being blocked by
OL,11,Fboth sides.
OL,13,FAround 65% of the jet fuel used in the
OL,14,FUK is imported, with a significant
OL,15,Fportion coming from the Middle East.
OL,17,FIn April, the International Energy
OL,18,FAgency said Europe had "maybe six
OL,19,Fweeks" of jet fuel left and warned of
OL,20,Ffuture flight cancellations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
